# unit/

BATS unit test suite for Intent CLI commands and functionality. Tests are organized by command category with shared helpers, setup/teardown handling, and comprehensive assertion utilities.

## Files

- `test_helper.bash` -- Shared test utilities, assertions, and test project creation helpers
- `basic.bats` -- Infrastructure smoke tests for test setup and CLI basics
- `global_commands.bats` -- Global commands (help, doctor, version, bootstrap, info)
- `bootstrap.bats` -- intent bootstrap command for global config initialization
- `config.bats` -- Configuration loading, PROJECT_ROOT detection, legacy project support
- `init_commands.bats` -- intent init command for new project creation
- `project_commands.bats` -- Commands requiring project context (st list, info)
- `st_commands.bats` -- Steel thread commands (st new, st list, sequential ID generation)
- `help_commands.bats` -- Help command with categories, descriptions, and command-specific help
- `agent_commands.bats` -- intent claude subagents commands (list, install, sync)
- `skills_commands.bats` -- intent claude skills commands (list, install, sync, uninstall, show)
- `fileindex_commands.bats` -- intent_fileindex command for file listing with recursion and filtering
- `treeindex_commands.bats` -- intent_treeindex command for .treeindex generation and validation
- `test_autopsy.bats` -- intent-autopsy skill with full directory install (ST0021)
- `test_diogenes.bats` -- diogenes subagent and intent-elixir-testing skill tests
